STATE of North Carolina
v.
Frederick Benjamin McQUAIG. No. 612P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2005. Adrian M. Lapas, Goldsboro, for Frederick McQuaig. Iain M. Stauffer, Associate Attorney General, James E. Hardin, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 8th day of December 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the orders of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of February 2005."
